-- Sonae Plans to Open More Than 25 Zippy Stores in Latin America
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-10-15T11:42:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-15/sonae-plans-to-open-more-than-25-zippy-stores-in-latin-america.html
Sonae (SON)  SGPS SA, a Portuguese
retailer, opened its first store in the Dominican Republic this
month and plans to have more than 25 stores in Latin America by
2016, the company said.  The store, part of the Zippy chain selling childrens’
clothing, opened in  Santo Domingo  through a franchising
agreement with the  Phoenix Group , the Maia, Portugal-based
company said today in an e-mailed statement.  “The expansion plan for Latin America forecasts the
opening of more than 25 stores until 2016” in countries such as
Venezuela, Colombia and Panama, according to Sonae.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
